{"doc":{"isMarkdown":false,"isTranslated":true,"isActive":true,"flaws":{},"title":"CustomEvent.initCustomEvent()","mdn_url":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/CustomEvent/initCustomEvent","locale":"zh-CN","native":"中文 (简体)","sidebarHTML":"<ol><li><strong><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Document_Object_Model\">Document Object Model</a></strong></li><li><strong><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/CustomEvent\"><code>CustomEvent</code></a></strong></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>Constructor</summary><ol><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/CustomEvent/CustomEvent\"><code>CustomEvent()</code></a></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>属性</summary><ol><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/CustomEvent/detail\"><code>detail</code></a></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>方法</summary><ol><li><svg class=\"icon icon-deprecated\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-deprecated\"></use>\n</svg><em><code>initCustomEvent()</code></em></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>继承</summary><ol><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Event\"><code>Event</code></a></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>Related pages for DOM</summary><ol><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/AbortController\"><code>AbortController</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/AbortSignal\"><code>AbortSignal</code></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/AbstractRange\"><code>AbstractRange</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Attr\"><code>Attr</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/CDATASection\"><code>CDATASection</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/CharacterData\"><code>CharacterData</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Comment\"><code>Comment</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/DOMError\"><code>DOMError</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/DOMException\"><code>DOMException</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/DOMImplementation\"><code>DOMImplementation</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/DOMParser\"><code>DOMParser</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/DOMPoint\"><code>DOMPoint</code></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/DOMPointReadOnly\"><code>DOMPointReadOnly</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/DOMRect\"><code>DOMRect</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/DOMTimeStamp\"><code>DOMTimeStamp</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/DOMTokenList\"><code>DOMTokenList</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Document\"><code>Document</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/DocumentFragment\"><code>DocumentFragment</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/DocumentType\"><code>DocumentType</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Element\"><code>Element</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Event\"><code>Event</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/EventTarget\"><code>EventTarget</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/HTMLCollection\"><code>HTMLCollection</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/MutationObserver\"><code>MutationObserver</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/NamedNodeMap\"><code>NamedNodeMap</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Node\"><code>Node</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/NodeIterator\"><code>NodeIterator</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/NodeList\"><code>NodeList</code></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/ProcessingInstruction\"><code>ProcessingInstruction</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Range\"><code>Range</code></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/StaticRange\"><code>StaticRange</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Text\"><code>Text</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/TextDecoder\"><code>TextDecoder</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/TextEncoder\"><code>TextEncoder</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/TimeRanges\"><code>TimeRanges</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/TreeWalker\"><code>TreeWalker</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/XMLDocument\"><code>XMLDocument</code></a></li></ol></details></li></ol>","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p></p><div class=\"notecard deprecated\" id=\"sect1\"><p><strong>已废弃:</strong> 该特性已经从 Web 标准中删除，虽然一些浏览器目前仍然支持它，但也许会在未来的某个时间停止支持，请尽量不要使用该特性。</p></div><p></p>\n\n<p><code><strong>CustomEvent.initCustomEvent()</strong></code> 方法初始化了一个&nbsp;<code>CustomEvent</code> object. 如果该事件已经被分发出去，则不会在初始化过程中重复触发．</p>\n\n<p>这类对象一定是由 <a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Document/createEvent\"><code>Document.createEvent()</code></a> 方法创建的。该方法被分发之前必须通过<a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/EventTarget/dispatchEvent\"><code>EventTarget.dispatchEvent()</code></a>方法设置．一旦被分发则，则无法被重新设置．</p>\n\n<div class=\"note notecard\" id=\"sect2\">\n<p><strong>该方法已经作废，不要在新项目中继续使用该方法。</strong></p>\n\n<p>Instead use specific event constructors, like <a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/CustomEvent/CustomEvent\" title=\"CustomEvent()\"><code>CustomEvent()</code></a>. The page on&nbsp;<a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/Events/Creating_and_triggering_events\">Creating and triggering events</a> gives more information about the way to use these.</p>\n</div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"syntax","title":"Syntax","isH3":false,"content":"<pre class=\"syntaxbox notranslate\"><em>event</em>.initCustomEvent(<em>type</em>, <em>canBubble</em>, <em>cancelable</em>, <em>detail</em>);\n</pre>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"parameters","title":"Parameters","isH3":true,"content":"<dl>\n <dt id=\"type\"><code><em>type</em></code></dt>\n <dd>类型<a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/conflicting/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/String_6fa58bba0570d663099f0ae7ae8883ab\"><code>DOMString</code></a>，事件名称。</dd>\n <dt id=\"canbub\"><em><code>canBub</code></em><em><code>ble</code></em></dt>\n <dd>类型<a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Boolean\"><code>Boolean</code></a>，事件是否沿着 dom 树向上冒泡。</dd>\n <dt id=\"cancelable\"><code><em>cancelable</em></code></dt>\n <dd>类型<a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Boolean\"><code>Boolean</code></a>，事件是否可取消。</dd>\n <dt id=\"deta\"><em><code>deta</code></em><em><code>il</code></em></dt>\n <dd>事件初始化时传入的数据。</dd>\n</dl>"}},{"type":"specifications","value":{"title":"Specifications","id":"specifications","isH3":false,"specifications":[{"bcdSpecificationURL":"https://dom.spec.whatwg.org/#dom-customevent-initcustomevent","title":"DOM Standard"}],"query":"api.CustomEvent.initCustomEvent"}},{"type":"browser_compatibility","value":{"title":"Browser compatibility","id":"browser_compatibility","isH3":false,"query":"api.CustomEvent.initCustomEvent","dataURL":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/CustomEvent/initCustomEvent/bcd.json"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"see_also","title":"See also","isH3":false,"content":"<ul>\n <li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/CustomEvent\"><code>CustomEvent</code></a></li>\n <li>The constructor to use instead of this deprecated method: <a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/CustomEvent/CustomEvent\" title=\"CustomEvent()\"><code>CustomEvent()</code></a>.</li>\n</ul>"}}],"toc":[{"text":"Syntax","id":"syntax"},{"text":"Specifications","id":"specifications"},{"text":"Browser compatibility","id":"browser_compatibility"},{"text":"See also","id":"see_also"}],"summary":"CustomEvent.initCustomEvent() 方法初始化了一个 CustomEvent object. 如果该事件已经被分发出去，则不会在初始化过程中重复触发．","popularity":0,"modified":"2022-07-19T02:29:32.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"CustomEvent.initCustomEvent()","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"},{"title":"CustomEvent.initCustomEvent()","locale":"fr","native":"Français"},{"title":"CustomEvent.initCustomEvent()","locale":"ja","native":"日本語"}],"source":{"folder":"zh-cn/web/api/customevent/initcustomevent","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/blob/main/files/zh-cn/web/api/customevent/initcustomevent/index.html","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/commit/5fe4ab11259b37914fab41914e84897fea47d143","filename":"index.html"},"parents":[{"uri":"/zh-CN/docs/Web","title":"Web 开发技术"},{"uri":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API","title":"Web API 接口参考"},{"uri":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/CustomEvent","title":"CustomEvent"},{"uri":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/CustomEvent/initCustomEvent","title":"CustomEvent.initCustomEvent()"}],"pageTitle":"CustomEvent.initCustomEvent() - Web API 接口参考 | MDN","noIndexing":false}}